title: Five ace fund managers join hands to launch new age financial services - Economic Times
content: Five ace fund managers join hands to launch new age financial services  Economic Times
description: This may be the first after a three year gap that top executives from financial services are taking a plunge into entrepreneurship after former Deutsche Bank executives like Bhupinder Singh of and Gunit Chadha who floated non-banking finance companies including InCred and APAC Financial.
